article_title: Wichita Orpheum Theatre announces new leader
article_text:
The Wichita Orpheum Theatre announced Diana Gordon as the next leader of the non-profit organization.

The board of directors appointed Gordon as President and Chief Development Officer, effective January 18.

Gordon brings 25 years of experience in the non-profit sector, and is a licensed Certified Fundraising Executive (CFRE) with special expertise in fundraising for arts & cultural organizations.

To learn more about the Orpheum, click here.
